OL,3,CMan murdered elderly stepfather before
OL,4,Ctrying to stab child
OL,6,FA knife-wielding murderer who stabbed
OL,7,Fhis stepfather in the neck was
OL,8,Feventually caught after being
OL,9,F"subdued" with a set of step ladders -
OL,10,Fwhile trying to stab a child.
OL,12,FAndrew Hall, 59, was armed with two
OL,13,Fknives when he stabbed Geoffrey Ives,
OL,14,F75, four times in the neck at his home
OL,15,Fin Heywood, Greater Manchester in
OL,16,FJanuary 2023.
