OL,6,FLeaving Mr Ives bleeding to death he
OL,7,Fthen took a taxi to Middleton where he
OL,8,Fsmashed his way into his ex-partner's
OL,9,Fhome, still armed with both knives,
OL,10,Fone of which was covered in Mr Ives'
OL,11,Fblood.
OL,13,FSix children in the house barricaded
OL,14,Fthemselves into a bedroom upstairs
OL,15,Fbefore one of the older brothers
OL,16,Ftackled Hall and subdued him with a
OL,17,Fset of step ladders.
