OL,6,FHall, from Rochdale, was found guilty
OL,7,Fof murder and aggravated burglary
OL,8,Fafter a trial at Manchester Minshull
OL,9,FStreet Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe was sentenced to 28 years for
OL,12,Fmurder and six years for aggravated
OL,13,Fburglary.
OL,15,FGeoffrey Ives was the partner of
OL,16,FHall's mother, who died in 2016, and
OL,17,Fsince her death Hall and Mr Ives had
OL,18,Fremained friends.
