OL,6,FInvestigating Officer and Temporary
OL,7,FDetective Superintendent David Moores
OL,8,Fsaid: "We will never really know what
OL,9,Fmotivated Hall to attack Geoffrey on
OL,10,Fthat night in question, but after
OL,11,Fdiscovering a murder scene, Hall's
OL,12,Fblazingly disregard, and lack of care
OL,13,Fmeant he kept reoffending in the local
OL,14,Farea causing a direct threat to the
OL,15,Fpublic.
