OL,6,F"Thanks to a swift response to those
OL,7,Fincidents from our local officers we
OL,8,Fwere able to detain him and after
OL,9,Fsecuring evidence from body worn video
OL,10,Fwhich raised suspicions as well as
OL,11,Fpainstakingly tracking his movements
OL,12,Fon CCTV, we were able to prove that he
OL,13,Fwas responsible for this horrific act
OL,14,Fwhere he took the life a much-loved
OL,15,Ffamily figure.
